verbose_text: As shown in XREF_FIG, in DRG neurons treated with TNF-alpha (40 ng/ml), synthetic cannabinoid WIN-55 (100, 200, 300 and 400 ng/ml) concentration- and time-dependently abolished TNF-alpha-induced expression of nNOS, with WIN-55 at 400 ng/ml completely abolishing the effect of TNF-alpha.
